jsat.linear.vectorcollection

Class DefaultVectorCollectionFactory<V extends Vec>

  • java.lang.Object
    • jsat.linear.vectorcollection.DefaultVectorCollectionFactory<V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, VectorCollectionFactory<V>

    public class DefaultVectorCollectionFactory<V extends Vec>
extends java.lang.Object
implements VectorCollectionFactory<V>
    DefaultVectorCollectionFactory is a generic factory that attempts to return a good vector collection for the given input. It may take into account the size of the data set, dimensions, and the distance metric in use to select a Vector Collection that will have the highest overall performance.
